  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK808">
<l>kēḷiḻukkaṅ kēḷāk keḻutakaimai vallārkku</l>
<l>nāḷiḻukka naṭṭār ceyiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To those who understand that by which they should not listen to (tales about) the faults of their friends, that is a (profitable) day on which the latter may commit a fault.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
